 Maina  Maina, who was declared wanted by a court of competent jurisdiction, was arrested on the night of November 30, 2020, through collaborative efforts of the police, INTERPOL NCB, Abuja, and their Nigerien counterpart. Force Public Relations Officer, DCP Frank Mba, who made the revelation in a statement yesterday in Abuja, said Maina is currently in a detention facility in the Niger Republic.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .